      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "PMC12755470",
      "text_span_id": "introduction_3",
      "text": "obesity and weight gain were risk factors and associated with poor prognosis of BC and the mechanisms for this connection may be related to resistance to insulin, chronic hyperinsulinemia, local inflammation, adipokine secretion, such as leptin (LEP), and more exposure of estrogen",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
